headline: Ecolab Schedules Webcast and Conference Call on February 10, 2026
summary: ST. PAUL, Minn., January 05, 2026--Ecolab will host a live webcast to discuss its 2025 fourth quarter results. A news release containing fourth quarter results is expected to be issued before market open on February 10, 2026.
